OL,3,CPolice 'short-changed' #900k by
OL,4,Cgovernment over Donald Trump's state
OL,5,Cvisit
OL,7,FThames Valley Police were "short-
OL,8,Fchanged" by almost #1m by the Home
OL,9,FOffice following Donald Trump's visit
OL,10,Fto Windsor last year.
OL,12,FThat's according to Matthew Barber,
OL,13,FPolice & Crime Commissioner, who has
OL,14,Fwritten to the government agency,
OL,15,Fdemanding a change in the "flawed
OL,16,Ffunding arrangements" of state visits
OL,17,Fto the town.
