OL,3,CPolice 'short-changed' #900k by
OL,4,Cgovernment over Donald Trump's state
OL,5,Cvisit
OL,7,FMr Barber said that whilst the Home
OL,8,FOffice covers the cost of equipment
OL,9,Fhire, it doesn't fund the actual cost
OL,10,Fof officer time for the force hosting
OL,11,Fthe event.
OL,13,FThis means Thames Valley Police are
OL,14,Funable to reclaim around #900,000 for
OL,15,FPresident Trump's visit last
OL,16,FSeptember, known as Op Liberty.
