OL,7,FMeanwhile, other local police forces
OL,8,Fwho send officers across the country
OL,9,Fto support these events can reclaim
OL,10,Fthe cost of their police officers'
OL,11,Ftime.
OL,13,FMatthew Barber said local council tax
OL,14,Fpayers in the Thames Valley are also
OL,15,Fbeing left short-changed, as officers
OL,16,Fare being "drawn away" from other
OL,17,Fpolicing duties.
