OL,5,Cvisit
OL,7,FThe Police & Crime Commissioner
OL,8,Frecognised that the force has a "proud
OL,9,Fhistory" of policing moments of
OL,10,Fnational importance but said the
OL,11,Ffrequency of state visits in Berkshire
OL,12,Fhas increased, whilst Buckingham
OL,13,FPalace undergoes refurbishment.
OL,15,FMr Barber said despite this, the
OL,16,FMetropolitan Police still receive a
OL,17,Fshare of more than #250m in capital
OL,18,Fcities grants, which helps the police
OL,19,Fto deal with the extra burden of large-
OL,20,Fscale events.
