OL,7,FIn a statement, the Home Office said:
OL,8,F"We and the police have long standing
OL,9,Farrangements in place to ensure state
OL,10,Fvisits are run safely and securely,
OL,11,Fwhile regular policing continues
OL,12,Facross communities.
OL,14,F"Thames Valley Police will receive
OL,15,Fadditional costs linked to this state
OL,16,Fvisit, and these will be recovered
OL,17,Fthrough standard major event
OL,18,Fprocedures."
